ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Brome-Missisquoi - Quebec ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE BROME-MISSISQUOI, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of the district of the Chambre de commerce de Brome-Missisquoi from Cowansville, Dunham, Frelighsburg, Saint-Armand, Brome, Bromont, Abercorn, Canton de Bedford, Bedford, Brigham, East-Farnham, Notre-Dame-de-Stanbridge, Pike River, Saint-Ignace-de-Stanbridge, Stranbridge-East, Stanbridge Station, and Sutton to Farnham, Sainte-Sabine, Lac-Brome, Sainte-Brigide-d'Iberville, Cowansville, Dunham, Frelighsburg, Saint-Armand, Brome, Bromont, Brigham, Abercorn, Canton de Bedford, Bedford, East-Farnham, Notre-Dame-de-Stanbridge, Pike River, Saint-Ignace-de-Stanbridge, Stanbridge-East, Stanbridge Station and Sutton.
